data.description: Beautiful, Beautiful property, this beautiful property completely remodeled in one of the most spectacular areas in all of Southern Florida, Cutler Bay, close to the Florida Turnpike and also the Southland Mall. This property has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a beautiful pool and terrace. It also has 2 storage  rooms and a laundry room. It has a very spacious drive way. Come and make this beautiful property your next home. Moving Home will be remove before closing
